dct_title_s: Nord- & Mittel-Asien : übersicht des Russischen Reiches
dct_description_sm: Map of Russia and central Asia, with Japan and part of China; relief shown by hachures and spot heights. "Ausgabe 1901." In upper margin: Stielers Hand-Atlas, no. 56. Probably issued in: Stielers Hand-Atlas ... 9., von Grund aus neubearb. und neugestochene Aufl. Gotha : Justus Perthes, 1905.
dct_spatial_sm: Russia. Russian Empire. Soviet Union. Former Soviet Republics
